                        Padding="10,0"
                        FontSize="Small"
                        HorizontalTextAlignment="Center"
                        Text="All of this selection look great and can be kept as an interactive pet or as part of a larger living terrarium/feature terrarium. The husbandry is simple, making them a great choice for beginners or young keepers."
                        TextColor="White" />
                </StackLayout>

